kubernetes as orchestration tool, used for microservices small apps 
its architeture - 2 entities master and worker node
api- application programming interface 
scheduler - for placements of pods 
controller manager - keeps tracks of tasks 
etcd - backup and restore , memory of k8s
nodes - its a vm where 1 pods = 1 containers 
kubelet - talks to api for the pods informations
service proxy - user commjnications for the services
pods - smallest units in k8s
kubectl is a tool for communication purpose 


